> it might hold up, plastic (Lincoln) versus metal (Century)) whether it takes

hmmm, my Lincoln has metal feed rollers, maybe they had too many
complaints or something.

got mine at a local welding house that was moving and selling stuff at
good prices so they didn't have to move it to their new location. 

YMMV

